is the email restoration tool always available stanford answers stanford university stanford answers is the email restoration tool always available categories accounts and ids administrative applications anti virus and security computer operating systems connecting to the network desktop hardware and support email and calendar help desk restricted information on it services software at stanford stanford hospital and clinics telephones and cable tv unix systems and software web services user login login with your sunet id home is the email restoration tool always available search this site not always you can request an email restore for email that's stored on the central email server between 7am and 7pm you cannot submit a request for a restore between 7pm and 7am when the server is scheduled for nightly backup the server can only process one restore at a time and will reject a request if there is another restore that's in progress if your restore request is not accepted initiate another request at a later time restored folders older than 7 days are removed automatically you can delete your restored folder at any time before the 7 day deadline the lost email page has more information about retrieving wayward email if you need more help submit a helpsu request or call 5 help stanford email stanford university 450 serra mall stanford california 94305 650 723 2300 terms of use copyright complaints
